mchorse.mappet.api.scripts.user.logs

Interface IMappetLogger


  • public interface IMappetLogger
    This interface represents Mappet logger.

    Use IScriptFactory.getLogger() to get Mappet logger instance.

    
    var logger = mappet.getLogger();

    logger.info("Hello world!");
